OL,3,CThree sisters 'betrayed' by government
OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Lise McNally spoke to
OL,8,Fthe three sisters
OL,10,FThree sisters say they feel "betrayed"
OL,11,Fafter the government announced women
OL,12,Fborn in the 1950s will not receive
OL,13,Fstate pension compensation.
OL,15,FAround 3.5 million women who were on
OL,16,Fthe cusp of retirement, or heading
OL,17,Ftowards it, were affected when the
OL,18,Fchanges to the state pension age rose
OL,19,Ffrom 60 to 65.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
