OL,3,CThree sisters 'betrayed' by government
OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,FThe sisters, from Cleveleys, in
OL,7,FLancashire, have spent years fighting
OL,8,Ffor their peers as part of campaign
OL,9,Fgroup Women Against State Pension
OL,10,FInequality (Waspi) and say those
OL,11,Faffected did not get enough time to
OL,12,Fprepare.
OL,14,FDespite an ombudsman recommending
OL,15,Fcompensation be paid the prime
OL,16,Fminister says it would cost the
OL,17,Fcountry billions, which taxpayers
OL,18,Fsimply cannot afford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
