OL,3,CThree sisters 'betrayed' by government
OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,F"They just want us to die, to go
OL,7,Fquietly and die," Norma Elkington, 67,
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"We've been going to demonstrations in
OL,11,FLondon, and demonstrating in the cold
OL,12,Fand the rain, we're doing it because
OL,13,Fwe want to defend the weak.
OL,15,F"We met women there who have had to
OL,16,Fsell their homes, where they've lived
OL,17,Fall their lives. They've had to sell
OL,18,Ftheir possessions."
