OL,3,CThree sisters 'betrayed' by government
OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,FThe women are some of thousands who,
OL,7,Fon the cusp of retirement, were sent
OL,8,Fletters telling them they would have
OL,9,Fto wait longer than they expected to
OL,10,Freceive their state pensions.
OL,12,FThe move was to bring women in line
OL,13,Fwith the retirement age for men.
OL,15,FBut Susan Dutton, 69, says it did not
OL,16,Fleave enough time to plan financially:
OL,17,F"Just think, getting to 66 and finding
OL,18,Fout, oh no, you're now not getting
OL,19,Fthat till 73, 74, how would they feel
OL,20,Fabout that?"
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@LO]
