OL,3,CThree sisters 'betrayed' by government
OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,FWhile Mary Waterhouse, 72, says others
OL,7,Fdid not get long enough to look for
OL,8,Fmore age-appropriate work.
OL,10,F"I was a carer and I was hoisting
OL,11,Fpeople in and out of bed," she said.
OL,12,F"I have my own problems with arthritis
OL,13,Fand I started to wonder who was the
OL,14,Fcarer and who was the cared-for?"
OL,16,FWaspi campaigners say 3.8 million
OL,17,Fpeople were not properly warned of the
OL,18,Fchanges, and demanded #10,000 per
OL,19,Fperson.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@aO]
