OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,FIn a report this year, the
OL,7,FParliamentary and Health Service
OL,8,FOmbudsman (PHSO) recommend the women
OL,9,Fshould be compensated, with payments
OL,10,Fof between #1,000 and nearly #3,000.
OL,12,FBut Work and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,13,FKendall announced on Monday the
OL,14,Fgovernment had rejected the
OL,15,FOmbudsman's suggestion of a flat rate
OL,16,Fpayout, partly because it would cost
OL,17,Fup to #10.5 billion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
