OL,3,CThree sisters 'betrayed' by government
OL,4,Cover no Waspi pension payout
OL,6,FHowever, she did accept the finding of
OL,7,Fmaladministration and has apologised
OL,8,Ffor a 28-month delay in writing to
OL,9,Faffected women.
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said she
OL,12,Funderstood the Waspi women's
OL,13,Fdisappointment, but said the ombudsman
OL,14,Frecommendations found "around 90% of
OL,15,Fwomen did know these changes were
OL,16,Fcoming" and added "as chancellor, I
OL,17,Fhave to account for every penny of
OL,18,Ftaxpayers' money spent".
