OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer, Deputy Prime
OL,7,FMinister and Ashton-under-Lyne MP
OL,8,FAngela Rayner, along with Rachel
OL,9,FReeves, are among senior ministers who
OL,10,Fbacked the Waspi campaign when Labour
OL,11,Fwas in opposition.
OL,13,FSomething Conservative leader Kemi
OL,14,FBadenoch was keen to point out at
OL,15,FPrime Minister Questions: "For years
OL,16,Fthe Prime Minister and his cabinet
OL,17,Fplayed politics with the Waspi women.
